%N A016010 Inverse of 2001st cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A016010 Periodic with period length 2001. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A016010 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A016010/b016010.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000</a>
%H A016010 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 2001.
%H A016010 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1232">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1232.
%H A016010 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A016010 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A016010 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[2001,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Sep 26 2020 *)
%o A016010 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(2001)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
%K A016010 sign,easy,changed
%O A016010 0,30
%A A016010 _Simon Plouffe_
